/>\n講到香港所有嘢都係要靠強国先可以生存"},{"pid":"62d168faf8625accd1b29ceca6104cd79d05a0ab","tid":2389543,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9713aaa5aebbcdaa7f201510380341a2c0500f23","tid":2389543,"uid":121146,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T03:50:48.000Z","msg":"香港97年前已經係國際金融中心  <br />\n21年居然可以比港共搞到若非爲中國白手套則甚麼都不是  變成一個內地城市  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:01:22.000Z","msg":"中國一窮二白 香港已經係國際金融中心"},{"pid":"6fd47c8ef9cd569c96718014ed7ca75973fc8450","tid":2389543,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:01:26.000Z","msg":"任白頭係咪老人痴呆，講野1999嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f665213fc5d8ae4279c326cb71fc58293d856e4","tid":2389543,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於有部份人批評香港內地化，但他指若沒有內地集資者來香港集資、吸引海外資金，香港沒有角色可以扮演。 </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n內地化同大陸黎唔黎香港集資有乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f8be189d274cdd9aad343d8595e553c3bf74a0","tid":2389543,"uid":278570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"內地化係吸多左外資定係嚇走外資先<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324c4f92e513021ee280087ed961e88942480033","tid":2389543,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:24:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">佢奶到咁，我更相信點解救屎三俠唯獨佢咁撚幸運唔洗坐！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"17759238a572481197475cf27de0fcd498f27f42","tid":2389543,"uid":325586,"like":0,"dislike":0